*FvwmButtonsRows 1
*FvwmButtonsPadding 0 0
*FvwmButtonsFont -adobe-helvetica-medium-r-*-*-12-*-*-*-*-*-*-*

*FvwmButtons(3x1, Container(Rows 2))
